<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify Your Email</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background-color: #10B981; color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
        .content { background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
        .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 30px; background-color: #10B981; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .code { background-color: #e5e7eb; padding: 15px; text-align: center; font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: 5px; font-weight: bold; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
        .warning { color: #EF4444; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 20px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Verify Your Email Address</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hi {{userName}},</h2>
            <p>Thank you for registering with {{appName}}! To complete your registration, please verify your email address by clicking the button below:</p>
            
            <a href="{{verificationUrl}}" class="button">Verify Email Address</a>
            
            <p>Or copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
            <p style="word-break: break-all; color: #4F46E5;">{{verificationUrl}}</p>
            
            <p class="warning">⚠️ This link will expire in 24 hours for security reasons.</p>
            
            <p>If you didn't create an account with {{appName}}, please ignore this email.</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>The {{appName}} Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} {{appName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
